perations\"}. Configure human-in-the-loop checkpoints.\n542 |                   </p>\n543 |                 </div>\n544 | \n545 |                 {/* Roadmap Step 3 */}\n546 |                 <div className=\"space-y-2 relative pl-6 border-l border-emerald-500/30\">\n547 |                   <div className=\"absolute -left-[6px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(16,185,129,0.8)]\" />\n548 |                   <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-400 font-mono\">PHASE 3: DAYS 61 - 90</span>\n549 |                   <h4 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Production Scale & Token Optimization</h4>\n550 |                   <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed\">\n551 |                     Scale agents to address {answers.topPriorities[1] || \"additional targets\"}. Perform final optimization checks via GFF Operational Dashboard.\n552 |                   </p>\n553 |                 </div>\n554 | \n555 |               </div>\n556 |             </div>\n557 | \n558 |             {/* Reset / Start Over Button */}\n559 |             <div className=\"pt-4 flex justify-end\">\n560 |               <button\n561 |                 type=\"button\"\n562 |                 onClick={() => {\n563 |                   setStep(1);\n564 |                   setAnswers({\n565 |                     industry: \"\",\n566 |                     companySize: \"\",\n567 |                     topPriorities: [],\n568 |                     aiJourney: \"\",\n569 |                     dataReadiness: \"\",\n570 |                     leadershipCommitment: \"\",\n571 |                     biggestChallenge: \"\",\n572 |                     email: \"\",\n573 |                     otp: \"\",\n574 |                     budget: \"\",\n575 |                     geography: \"\",\n576 |                   });\n577 |                   setOtpSent(false);\n578 |                   setEnteredOtp(\"\");\n579 |                   setReportGenerated(false);